本公司的地底光纖，部分將軍澳的寬頻及家居電話服務因而受到影響。我們現正全力搶修，務求儘快令服務回復正常。不便之處，敬請見諒。<br />\n<br />\n對於近日有政府部門(水務署、路政署及土木工程拓展署)工程人員於工程進行時，懷疑未有完全依從有關工作指引而掘斷了本公司的地底光纖電纜，以致影響我們對客戶的服務，對此我們深表關注。我們會與有關政府部門積極商討，務求他們加強其工程水平，以及找出可妥善減少出錯的方法。對於受影響的客戶，我們深表抱歉。<br />\n<br />\nThis afternoon at around 1.20pm our fibre cable was accidentally damaged by the works of Civil Engineering and Development Department. Our broadband and home telephone service at some parts of Tseung Kwan O is therefore affected. We are carrying out immediate maintenance with a view to resuming our service as soon as possible. We apologise for any inconvenience caused.<br />\n<br />\nWe are highly concerned about the recent incidents in which our fibre cables were damaged by the works of government departments (Water Supplies Department, Highways Department and Civil Engineering and Development Department), a suspected result of failing to fully adhere to the work permit guidelines. We will proactively discuss with the related government departments, seeking their improvements in works standard and miminising faults. We apologise to our affected customers.<br />\n<br />\nHKBN FB咁寫"},{"pid":"97100d9890cab25853944841cc746e962074c6a1","tid":1782580,"uid":228945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c69ded6b80952d4294b721f4201ce183202393a2","tid":1782580,"uid":284951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T08:51:54.000Z","msg":"今日下午約一時二十分土木工程拓展署的工程人員懷疑意外掘斷了本公司的地底光纖，部分將軍澳的寬頻及家居電話服務因而受到影響。我們現正全力搶修，務求儘快令服務回復正常。不便之處，敬請見諒。<br />\n<br />\n對於近日有政府部門(水務署、路政署及土木工程拓展署)工程人員於工程進行時，懷疑未有完全依從有關工作指引而掘斷了本公司的地底光纖電纜，以致影響我們對客戶的服務，對此我們深表關注。我們會與有關政府部門積極商討，務求他們加強其工程水平，以及找出可妥善減少出錯的方法。對於受影響的客戶，我們深表抱歉。<br />\n<br />\nThis afternoon at around 1.20pm our fibre cable was accidentally damaged by the works of Civil Engineering and Development Department. Our broadband and home telephone service at some parts of Tseung Kwan O is therefore affected. We are carrying out immediate maintenance with a view to resuming our service as soon as possible. We apologise for any inconvenience caused.<br />\n<br />\nWe are highly concerned about the recent incidents in which our fibre cables were damaged by the works of government departments (Water Supplies Department, Highways Department and Civil Engineering and Development Department), a suspected result of failing to fully adhere to the work permit guidelines. We will proactively discuss with the related government departments, seeking their improvements in works standard and miminising faults. We apologise to our affected customers.<br />\n<br />\nHKBN FB咁寫"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T09:06:54.000Z","msg":"政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c571ee62c05f300ec873ec4acb5334dc66ac3802","tid":1782580,"uid":23020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e43dd6ad6b7c2d7bf1a5e70d73c1e99e9a2d64d5","tid":1782580,"uid":23020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T05:53:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">NowTV / 網上行</span></span> 最新優惠<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nNowTV 新聞台 直播台<br />\n裝NowTV任何Plan即享呢兩個免費台<br />\n識睇 一定係睇Now新聞<br />\nWhatsapp : <a href=\"http://bit.ly/pccw_nowtv004\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2Fpccw_nowtv004&d=wPrcUaBjKD1L%2BB1JqNzGILhWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=4521f4a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/pccw_nowtv004</a><br />\nTelegram: <a href=\"http://bit.ly/PCCWNOWTV\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.